display_name: Bid transformation - 1000 - RAW test data sets_31 - Ariba Sourcing - 2

property_sql_factory_datasets.sql:
SELECT 
    'Bid_' || "Bid"."AlternativeId" as "ID",
    'RFXDocument_' || "Bid"."ContentDocumentReference_documentId" as "RFXDocument",
    "Bid"."AlternativeId" as "AlternativeId",
    "Bid"."AlternativeStatus" as "AlternativeStatus",
    CAST("Bid"."SliceType" AS INT) as "SliceType",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,"Bid"."SavedDate") as "SavedDate",
    "Bid"."SliceId" as "SliceId",
    "Bid"."IsEmailBid" as "IsEmailBid",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,"Bid"."SubmissionDate") as "SubmissionDate",
    "Bid"."IsSurrogateBid" as "IsSurrogateBid",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,"Bid"."TimeUpdated") as "TimeUpdated",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,"Bid"."ProcessedDate") as "ProcessedDate",
    TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,CAST("Bid"."TimeCreated" AS TIMESTAMP)) as "TimeCreated",
    "Bid"."Active" as "Active",
    "Bid"."AlternativeType" as "AlternativeType",
    "Bid"."ContentDocumentReference_UniqueName" as "ContectDocumentReferenceUniqueName",
    "Bid"."ContentDocumentReference_documentMinorVersion" as "ContectDocumentReferenceDocumentMinorVersion",
    "Bid"."ContentDocumentReference_documentVersion" as "ContectDocumentReferenceDocumentVersion",
    "Bid"."ContentDocumentReference_documentId" as "ContectDocumentReferenceDocumentId"
FROM "RFXBid" AS "Bid"
WHERE 1=1
    AND  "Bid"."Active" = 'true'
